                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Portland</placeName>\n                <date>July 20<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 1855</date>\n            </p>\n            <p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>, dear sir<lb/> After waiting a long time for\n                your<lb/> valuable <sic>piriodicle</sic>, at last it came<lb/> and am very much\n                pleased with it<lb/> and shall try my best to <sic>sprad</sic> its<lb/>\n                <sic>surculation</sic> in this far <placeName>Western Country</placeName>.<lb/> I am\n                happy to hear of your safe return<lb/> from your late tour to the\n                    <placeName>South-West</placeName>.<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr Leeser</persName> I must inform you that<lb/> after I got home my\n                Brother moved with<lb/> his <sic>famile</sic> to <placeName>San\n                    Francisco</placeName>, and is<lb/> now living there, in passing through the<lb/>\n                state he met <persName>Mrs <hi rend=\"underline\">Whitney</hi></persName>=<hi\n                    rend=\"underline\">Alias</hi>=<lb/>\n                <persName>Sarah Ansell</persName>, she complaind very<lb/> much about her Father,\n                She says that<lb/> she send him a Letter in which she Begged<lb/> his Pardon, but he\n                send the Letter back<lb/> unnoticed, <persName>Mr Leeser</persName> all they\n                    <add>?</add><lb/> I can write to you is about <sic>som</sic> Rich Gold<lb/>\n                Mines discovered about <sic>for</sic> Hundred miles<lb/> East of this Place which\n                one <sic>sayd</sic> to be<lb/> very Extensive, if all true we will have<lb/> a great\n                harvest, Business has been very good<lb/> since my Return and Expect better\n                times<lb/> yet, in this place are about 25 Jews<lb/> 2 familys, we are trying to\n                    <sic>git</sic> a Jewish</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3q52fz98/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
