                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>Burying ground. There are <sic>sum</sic> here who want<lb/> to wait a while\n                    <sic>yit</sic> so we are all healthy persons<lb/> but I think it is better to\n                prepare before<lb/> hand I have nothing more to write this time</p>\n            <p>I remain your <sic>respectfull</sic> Friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Moses Abrams</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>of the firm of <persName><hi rend=\"underline\">Abrams Brothers</hi></persName></p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
